## 3. Complete Gap Analysis

### 3.1 Critical Gaps — MUST ADD (P0)

#### GAP-001: Comments Table

| Attribute | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Gap** | No table for post comments |
| **Business Impact** | Users cannot comment on posts |
| **PRD Reference** | U-031: "As a user, I want to comment on posts" |
| **Recommendation** | Add `comments` table with nested reply support |

**Proposed Table Structure:**
```
comments
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── post_id (UUID, FK → posts)
├── user_id (UUID, FK → users)
├── parent_id (UUID, FK → comments, nullable for replies)
├── content (TEXT)
├── like_count (INTEGER)
├── is_hidden (BOOLEAN) — for moderation
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
├── updated_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

---

#### GAP-002: Admin Roles & Permissions System

| Attribute | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Gap** | Only single `role` field on users table |
| **Business Impact** | Cannot implement granular admin access control |
| **Task Requirement** | "Roles & permissions" entity |
| **Human Decision** | Three roles: super-admin, moderator, support |
| **Recommendation** | Add `admin_roles` and `admin_permissions` tables |

**Proposed Tables:**

**admin_roles:**
```
admin_roles
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── name (VARCHAR) — 'super_admin', 'moderator', 'support'
├── description (TEXT)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**admin_permissions:**
```
admin_permissions
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── role_id (UUID, FK → admin_roles)
├── permission (VARCHAR) — e.g., 'manage_users', 'moderate_content', 'view_reports', 'manage_payouts'
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**user_admin_roles (junction):**
```
user_admin_roles
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── user_id (UUID, FK → users)
├── role_id (UUID, FK → admin_roles)
├── assigned_by (UUID, FK → users)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**Permission Matrix (Recommended):**

| Permission | Super Admin | Moderator | Support |
|------------|-------------|-----------|---------|
| `manage_users` | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| `manage_creators` | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| `moderate_content` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| `review_reports` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| `resolve_reports` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| `manage_payouts` | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| `view_analytics` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| `manage_categories` | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| `manage_dmca` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| `ban_users` | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| `suspend_users` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| `view_transactions` | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ |
| `issue_refunds` | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| `manage_admins` | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |

