#### GAP-003: Content Tags/Hashtags

| Attribute | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Gap** | No way to tag or categorize individual posts |
| **Business Impact** | Limited content discovery |
| **PRD Reference** | Explore/Discover features |
| **Recommendation** | Add `tags` and `post_tags` tables |

**Proposed Tables:**

**tags:**
```
tags
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── name (VARCHAR, UNIQUE)
├── slug (VARCHAR, UNIQUE)
├── usage_count (INTEGER) — denormalized for performance
├── is_nsfw (BOOLEAN)
├── is_banned (BOOLEAN) — for prohibited tags
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**post_tags (junction):**
```
post_tags
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── post_id (UUID, FK → posts)
├── tag_id (UUID, FK → tags)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
├── UNIQUE(post_id, tag_id)
```

