#### GAP-004: Tip Goals

| Attribute | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **Gap** | Tips only tracked in transactions, no goal tracking |
| **Business Impact** | Creators cannot set tip goals for engagement |
| **Human Decision** | YES — track tip goals separately |
| **Recommendation** | Add `tip_goals` table |

**Proposed Table:**
```
tip_goals
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── creator_id (UUID, FK → creator_profiles)
├── title (VARCHAR) — e.g., "New Camera Fund"
├── description (TEXT)
├── target_amount (DECIMAL)
├── current_amount (DECIMAL) — denormalized for performance
├── status (VARCHAR) — 'active', 'completed', 'cancelled'
├── started_at (TIMESTAMP)
├── deadline_at (TIMESTAMP, nullable)
├── completed_at (TIMESTAMP, nullable)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
├── updated_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

**tip_goal_contributions:**
```
tip_goal_contributions
├── id (UUID, PK)
├── tip_goal_id (UUID, FK → tip_goals)
├── user_id (UUID, FK → users)
├── transaction_id (UUID, FK → transactions)
├── amount (DECIMAL)
├── created_at (TIMESTAMP)
```

